data.title: Revco - Milton, PA
data.meta_description: Store 1016, 901 Carpenter Rd; opened with the center most likely in the 70s based on store number.  Closed in 1997 immediately after the CVS merger; CVS has a larger store further in town and didn't appear to have an interest in one with almost nothing around it (which seems to still be a problem with this center).  According to the sign was most recently "Liberty Business Information", but is currently vacant.
